{
  "stem": "4272.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what I did, not even looking that maybe I'm doing it next to a German.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he said go, and I went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I-- I had somebody that took me to this village that he knew about, this man, because-- it's a long story.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was supposed to take a family's young child-- a little boy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They knew somebody in the village that was willing to save me with the boy, because they did it in order to save their child.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the day before he was going to come for me and that baby, they-- they had this thing that we-- we all went to the-- to the camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was too late.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when my sister got sick, then I-- I asked this man, whether was it possible that I am the one that was going to be there with the child and so on, would it be possible for him to help us?",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he agreed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How were you dressed when you left the labor camp?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- in the clothes that I had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have uniforms, if that's what you-- what you meant, no.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In whatever we had, that's what we wore, all the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not in the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't needed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were only Jews in the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Leave on my own?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that I escaped, nobody saw it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's how I escaped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That the group went-- made a left-- a right turn going to the camp, and I, by myself, turned away to the left.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when they were a little distance away, I ran across the street, and there were bushes, and I was hiding in the bushes, and then I walked out, you know, to the sidewalk to see whether I would see somebody.",
      "word_count": 41
    }
  ],
